    %h4 Community Guidelines
    %h5 It's simple. Be kind.
    %p
      As you know,
      %b we wake up in the morning to enable and encourage the dreams of others.
      We want you to feel like the world is a sandbox where you can create the life you have imagined,
      %b but only if the things you build do not infringe upon the dreams of others.
    %p
      The following actions and behaviours are absolutely not tolerated on our platform.  If you engage in or promote any of these, we will immediately suspend your account and ban you from Lumastic indefinitely.  We understand that many of these behaviours are subjective.  Although we will always engage in productive discourse on how these should be interpreted, we still make the final call about implementation of interpretations.  We also hold every right to ban or suspend your account in circumstances not directly correlated to any of the following behaviours.
